dev
Class DevicesResource

java.lang.Object
  org.restlet.Handler
      org.restlet.resource.Resource
          dev.DevicesResource

public class DevicesResource
extends org.restlet.resource.Resource

The DevicesResource is used by the NameServer to represent the list of online devices. Periodically, each device refreshes its entry in the resource. A new entry expires after some time, if not refreshed.

Author:
Mamta
